---
import HierarchyExplorer from './HierarchyExplorer';
---
<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-[var(--card)]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-[var(--fg)]">The 5-level spec hierarchy</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-[var(--muted)] mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Every RootSpec starts from first principles and cascades down to testable acceptance criteria.
    </p>
    <HierarchyExplorer client:load />
  </div>
</section>
